nges; Hook: “Gentle by design” - Mycelial Chorus: Fungal threads + soft pulses; Hook: “Underground orchestra” 4) Hooks/Angles for Impulse Merch Buyers (plant lovers) - “Wrap yourself in bloom season” - “For plants that hum—and humans who listen” - “Designed at the intersection of botany and sound” - “Your sofa’s new conversation piece” - “Textile art for the propagation-obsessed” - “Science-chic: proven vibes, elevated design” - “From pollinator buzz to cozy fringe” - “Minimal wave, maximal calm” - “A gift for the greenhouse heart” - “Slow mornings, soft waves, greener days” - “Vibes with receipts: research-inspired art” - “Plant room essential” - “Whisper-level comfort” - “A quiet orchestra in woven cotton” - “Honey-sweet, bee-inspired” - “For the Monstera maximalist” - “Tactile + technical = timeless” - “Nectar-level cozy” - “Tune your space, not just your plants” - “Because your plants aren’t the only ones growing” 5) YouTube/Content Engine + Lead Gen Channel Positioning: The Sound Garden – science-backed tips, cinematic plant visuals, relaxing soundscapes, and practical routines. Core Video Series - Plant Sound Lab: 10-min experiments (safe dB, frequency ranges, before/after timelapses) - Pollinator Stories: Bee-inspired episodes + nectar research explained - Setup Saturdays: Sound-friendly plant corners (distance, volume, routine) - Mythbust Mondays: Music myths vs. facts - Soundscapes: 1–3 hr gentle ambient tracks for plant rooms (monetizable) - Case Studies: Viewers’ plants featured with routine breakdowns Lead Magnet + Funnel - Lead Magnet: Free mini eBook (12 pages) + 3 free “Plant Room” audio tracks (mp3) + printable routine card - Opt-in: “Grow Mail” newsletter: weekly routines, deals, early art drops - CTA in videos: On-screen lower-third + end card “Get your free plant sound kit” - Landing Page: Simple, proof-forward, tasteful art - Tripwire: $9 Starter Pack (9 tracks, routine templates, eBook full version sampler) - Core Offer: $97 Plant Resonance Pro 