hones on Planters Work?, headphones plants, Mythbust, “Cute, mostly silly”, Free kit 36. The Science of Petal Resonance, petal resonance bee, Educate, “Microphones in petals?”, Pro Kit 37. Comparing Plant Apps and Audio Packs, plant audio app vs tracks, Buyer, “Subscriptions vs ownership”, Pro Kit 38. DIY Plant Sound Panels, DIY sound panels plant room, DIY, “Reduce echo, focus sound”, Merch tie-in 39. Sound for Seed Germination?, sound germination plants, Educate, “Early signals?”, Free kit 40. Your First 30-Day Sound Plan, 30-day plant sound plan, Practical, “Calendar included”, Starter Pack 41–100. [Continuing topics: species routines (Fiddle Leaf, Hoya, Calathea, Ferns, Philodendron, Alocasia), integration with grow lights, microgreens, balcony pollinators, safe nursery applications, case studies, Q&A, user submissions, UGC highlight reels, checklists, troubleshooting, gear comparisons, myths debunked, caregiver mindfulness, acoustics in small apartments, office plant sound, etc.] Note: Full 100-row spreadsheet is large—request and I’ll export the complete table CSV with all columns. 7) Offer Suite + $200K/Month Profit Plan (60 Days, 95%+ margin digital) Products (Digital, 95–99% margin) - $0 Free Plant Sound Starter (lead magnet): mini eBook + 3 tracks + routine card - $9 Starter Pack (tripwire): 9 tracks, 7-day plan, quick charts - $39 “Sound Garden Rooms”: 30 tracks curated by room mood (work, rest, morning) - $97 Plant Resonance Pro Kit: full eBook, 60 tracks, planner, checklists, species cards - $297 Lifetime Library + Updates + Design Pack (wallpapers, printable art, social templates) - $19/month Plant Audio Lab: monthly new tracks, routines, office hours, community - $997 Licensing Pack (B2B): nurseries/studios can play tracks in-store (annual license) Target P&L to $200K Profit/Month - Aim for $230K gross revenue, $20–$25K media/affiliates/tools, ~$205–$210K net (processing fees ~3% included) Illustrative Mix (first stable month by Day 60) - 1,500 units 